metadata.name: GET UP #1
metadata.description:
I'm so excited to present my Genesis drop song to my Sound.XYZ Family. I wrote this record the day after my grandfather passed away. I was feeling so low about everything in my life. This was a reminder and a motivator to myself and others who are experiencing trauma and ultimately a rough time. Life is a continuum. It keeps moving despite our lows. I encourage you to love yourself enough to move with the shift. One love. - TiKA

Get Up!
Written by TiKA
Produced by: TiKA & Cxleb
Additional production by: @CaseyMQ
Engineered + recorded by: @YogiDaProducer
